About Cowart Ranch
In 1986, our family started Cowart Ranch and Farms’ first endeavors in Flagler County, Fl. by forming The Blueberry Strand.  Since then, we’ve branched into selling our very own grass-fed beef, pasture raised eggs, and our fall Maze Dayz event with operations growing pumpkins, sunflowers, and family activities.
In 2012 Dalton and Brittany Kinney introduced Agri-tourism into our west Bunnell farming community by hosting Flagler Counties first annual “Maze Dayz,” a fun annual fall harvest festival!! Since then it’s become a family tradition for many to gather. This year it is scheduled on weekends this Oct 4-Nov 2, and weekdays for scheduled school groups. It’s held at The Blueberry Strand,
located at 8185 W. Highway 100 in Bunnell
. Check our more information about this by clicking on the tab labeled
Maze and Fall Festival.
We’d love to see smiles on your faces out here this year supporting your local farmers. Remember NO FARMS, NO FOOD!
Experience the Best of Agri-Tourism
From thrilling seasonal events to our cherished blueberry picking, Cowart Ranch and Farms offers a unique blend of agriculture and fun for everyone. Our commitment is rooted in creating memorable experiences that resonate with our community and visitors alike.
Where Farming Meets Community
Join us in celebrating the harvest! Our seasonal activities connect people with the joy of farming while ensuring transparency and quality in our grass-fed beef products.
Cowart Ranch and Farms
Together, we cultivate lasting connections, healthier lives, and enrich our community one experience at a time at Cowart Ranch and Farms.

Weddings and Events
We have two large barns, one with a temporary kitchen area, approximately 150 chairs available along with about 16, 8ft long banquet sized tables that are available to you upon rental.
Weddings and Receptions
Venue for your wedding, reception, or vow renewal. Outside catering aloud. Contact us to let us know what you would like to do and we can give you a price that will be reasonable for you.
Birthday parties
We have a lot to offer for birthday parties with plenty to do for the kids. Depending on what you want to include for your party, we can work it out and make a price good for you!
Events and parties
Company parties, Christmas Parties, Reunions, Fund Raisers
